scaledmarkets.dabl.analyzer

Class CompilerState

  • java.lang.Object
    • scaledmarkets.dabl.analyzer.CompilerState
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    ClientState, TaskContext

    public class CompilerState
extends java.lang.Object
    Contains the entire state of the compiler when processing an input file. When the compiler finishes processing a file, it returns the CompilerState.
